        <headline>Special Weather Statement issued March 31 at 7:16PM PDT by NWS Pendleton OR</headline>
        <description>At 716 PM PDT, Doppler radar was tracking a strong thunderstorm over
Mayville, or near Fossil, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Half inch hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor hail damage to vegetation is possible.

Locations impacted include...
Kinzua and Mayville.
</description>
        <instruction>If outdoors, consider seeking shelter inside a building.</instruction>
